---
layout: layouts/base.njk
---

{# Hero Section #}
<header class="text-center pt-12 pb-6 bg-neutral-100">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h1 class="text-4xl text-light leading-tighter mb-6">
      Unlocking your <span class="md:block"><span id="swapping-text" class="highlight">grantees’</span></span> research, simply
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl font-light text-neutral-600 mb-6 max-w-lg mx-auto">Find your articles, measure their openness, and take action to increase your OA policy compliance.</p>
    <a href="https://savvycal.com/Joe/ed52a37f" data-savvycal-embed class="inline-block bg-carnation-600 text-white mb-6 py-3 px-8 rounded-sm text-lg hover:bg-carnation-700 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105 focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-carnation-300">
      Schedule a demo →
    </a>
  </div>
</header>

{# Product Image Section #}
<section class="relative bg-neutral-100 pt-4 pb-0">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center relative z-10">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">
      Your data meets Open Data, <span class="md:block">shaped by expert analysis.</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto shadow-lg rounded-lg border border-dotted border-neutral-700 overflow-hidden z-20">
      <img src="/img/screenshot.png" alt="OA.Report Web Application Screenshot" class="mx-auto">
    </div>
  </div>
  {# Dark Background extension #}
  <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 bg-neutral-900 h-32 z-0 -mt-16"></div>
</section>

{# Trusted By Section #}
<section class="pt-8 pb-16 bg-neutral-900 text-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h2 class="text-center text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-200 mb-8">Trusted by leading research funders</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 justify-center items-center">
      {% for user in users %}
        {% if user.logo %}
        <p class="sr-only">{{ user.name }}</p>
        <a href="{{ user.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block h-12" title="Go to the {{ user.acronym }} website">
          {% set imgFile = "../" + user.logo %}
          {% set altText = "Logo for " + user.acronym  %}
          {% webpImg imgFile, altText, user.width, user.height, '', true %}
        </a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Testimonial Section #}
<section class="bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-900 py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 flex justify-center items-center">
    <div class="w-full max-w-6xl flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <p class="text-lg text-light mb-4">
          As seen in <a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-023-00175-1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1">Nature:<br>“Confused by open-access policies? These tools can help”</a>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-2xl text-light">
          “The Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation in Seattle, Washington, has invested US$1.8 million to support the development of OA.Report, a tool that helps funders to track awardee compliance with foundation open-access policies. Developed by OA.Works in London, OA.Report uses text-mining techniques to match articles with the funder that supported the work, by sifting through academic papers and open-access metadata.”
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <div class="w-32 h-auto mx-auto">
           <a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-023-00175-1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block">
            {% include 'svg/nature.svg' %}
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Schedule a Demo Section #}
<section class="bg-carnation-500 text-white py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8">Take a free tour of OA.Report</h2>
    <a href="https://savvycal.com/Joe/ed52a37f" data-savvycal-embed class="inline-block bg-white text-carnation-600 py-3 px-8 rounded-sm text-lg font-medium hover:bg-neutral-100 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105 focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-carnation-300">
      Get a demo
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

{# Features Section #}
<section class="bg-neutral-100 pt-24 pb-12">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-center text-2xl text-light mb-8">
      <span class="font-semibold">OA.Report</span> translates <span class="md:block"><span class="highlight">policy to practice</span></span> by helping funders and institutions:
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {% for feature in features %}
        <div class="p-6 bg-neutral-900 shadow-lg text-center rounded-xl">
          <div class="mx-auto mb-4">{% include feature.img %}</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-white">{{ feature.heading }}</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-300">{{ feature.subheading }}</p>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Testimonial Section #2 #}
<section class="bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-900 pt-12 pb-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 flex justify-center items-center">
    <div class="w-full max-w-6xl flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <div class="w-full lg:w-72 h-auto mx-auto">
          <img src="img/users/ashley-farley.jpg" alt="Ashley Farley" class="rounded-lg">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <p class="text-2xl text-light mb-4">
         “Open Access promotes access, transparency, and equity, enabling life-saving ideas to be shared, tested, and built upon globally. Tracking policy compliance is crucial for maximizing impact, which is why partnering with a like-minded mission-driven organization, such as OA.Works, is essential.”
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-light">
          — Ashley Farley<br> Senior Officer of Knowledge and Research Services<br> Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation 
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Include Glider.js CSS and JS #}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/glider-js@1/glider.min.css">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/glider-js@1/glider.min.js"></script>

{# Case Studies Section #}
<section class="bg-carnation-200 px-8 md:pl-8 md:pr-0 py-24">
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center lg:items-start"> 
      
      <div class="lg:w-1/3 mb-6 text-center md:text-left"> 
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8">Case studies</h2>
        <a href="https://savvycal.com/Joe/ed52a37f" data-savvycal-embed class="inline-block bg-navyBlue-600 text-white py-3 px-8 rounded-sm text-lg hover:bg-carnation-700 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105 focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-carnation-300">
          Schedule a demo →
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:w-2/3 relative overflow-visible">
        <div class="glider-contain">
          <div class="glider">
            {% for case in cases %}
            <div class="px-4">
              <div class="relative bg-neutral-100 shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition">
                <div class="relative w-full h-64">
                  <img src="{{ case.bg }}" alt="Background for {{ case.heading }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover filter grayscale brightness-50">
                  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-900 opacity-70"></div> 

                  <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center px-12">
                    <img src="{{ case.img }}" alt="{{ case.heading }}" class="w-36 h-auto object-contain mb-6"> 
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">{{ case.heading }}</h3>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
          <button class="glider-prev bg-white text-neutral-600 rounded-full px-4 py-2 shadow-md hover:bg-neutral-100 focus:outline-none">&larr;</button>
          <button class="glider-next bg-white text-neutral-600 rounded-full px-4 py-2 shadow-md hover:bg-neutral-100 focus:outline-none">&rarr;</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Init Glider #}
<script>
  new Glider(document.querySelector('.glider'), {
  slidesToShow: 1,
  dots: '.dots',
  draggable: true,
  arrows: {
    prev: '.glider-prev',
    next: '.glider-next'
  },
  responsive: [
    {
      breakpoint: 768, // At 768px and up
      settings: {
        slidesToShow: 2,
        slidesToScroll: 1
      }
    },
    {
      breakpoint: 1024, // At 1024px and up
      settings: {
        slidesToShow: 2,
        slidesToScroll: 1
      }
    }
  ]
});
</script>

{# Custom Glider styles #}
<style>
.glider-prev, .glider-next {
  margin-top: 1rem; /* Arrows now sit below images */
  text-align: center;
  display: inline-block;
  background-color: white;
  border-radius: 9999px;
  padding: 0.5rem;
  color: #333;
  font-size: 1em;
  box-shadow: 0px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  position: static;
}
.glider-prev:hover, .glider-next:hover {
  background-color: #f5f5f5;
}
</style>

{# Sign Up Section #}
<section class="bg-carnation-300 px-8 py-24" id="newsletter-signup">
  <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <div class="col-span-3 lg:col-span-1 lg:col-start-2">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8">Sign up for updates</h2>
        {% include 'partials/signup-form.njk' %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Partnership Section #}
<section class="bg-neutral-800 text-white py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 flex justify-center items-center">
    <div class="w-full max-w-6xl flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <div class="w-64 h-auto mx-auto">
          <a href="https://www.gatesfoundation.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Go to the BMGF website">
            {% include 'svg/bmgf.svg' %}
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-lg text-light mb-4">
          Our funders
        </h2>
        <p class="text-2xl text-light">
          Built in partnership with the <a href="https://blog.oa.works/grant-to-bolster-oa-policies-from-bmgf/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline underline-offset-2 md:underline-offset-8 decoration-1">Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation</a> with grant support from the <a href="https://blog.oa.works/grant-from-robert-wood-johnson-foundation/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline underline-offset-2 md:underline-offset-8 decoration-1">Robert Wood Johnson Foundation</a> & <a href="https://blog.oa.works/arcadia-fund-increases-support-for-our-work/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline underline-offset-2 md:underline-offset-8 decoration-1">Arcadia</a>.
